@startuml
title Activity Diagram: PDF Tools Operations

start
:User opens PDF Tools;
:Select PDF tool action;

if (Action == Convert to PDF) then (yes)
  :Select Word/Excel/Image file;
  :Send file to CloudConvert API;
  :Receive converted PDF;
elseif (Action == Merge PDFs) then (yes)
  :Select multiple PDF files;
  :Combine PDF pages into single stream;
elseif (Action == Split PDF) then (yes)
  :Select PDF and split criteria;
  :Extract pages to new PDF files;
endif

:Save resulting PDF(s) to Local Storage;
if (Save Success?) then (Yes)
  :Show result to User;
else (No)
  :Show Error;
endif

stop
@enduml
